title: SJW: A Day In The Life
text:
SJW: A Day In The Life A look at how Donald Trump's presidency has many Americans living in fear Infowars.com - February 21, 2017 Comments 
Social Justice Warrior Extraordinaire ‘Rainbow Snatch’ gives us a hard look into the life of what it takes to be a social justice warrior. 
Later on, Rainbow Snatch infiltrates the Infowars studio and rants about what it’s like to be an omni-sexual, trans binary, multidimensional being struggling with the reality that Donald Trump is now President of the United States.
